  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "MCAL Multi-Core Module Type I"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In this type, MCAL modules are available on a single core only, the interfaces are not globally available"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Type I = 1a + 2a + 3a"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/02_MCAL%20Multicore:%20Module%20types/image2022-12-30_16-25-1.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/02_MCAL Multicore_ Module types/image2022-12-30_16-25-1.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Example for this type is FLS, MEMIF and FEE"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "MCAL Multi-Core Module Type II"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In this type, MCAL modules provides a distributed kernel, executed per core, acting on individually mapped HW elements"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Type II = 1b + 2b + 3a"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/02_MCAL%20Multicore:%20Module%20types/image2022-12-30_16-26-4.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/02_MCAL Multicore_ Module types/image2022-12-30_16-26-4.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "MCAL Multi-Core Module Type III"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In this type, the MCAL modules provides a distributed kernel executed per core acting on globally available HW elements"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Type III = 1b + 2b + 3b"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/02_MCAL%20Multicore:%20Module%20types/image2022-12-30_16-27-56.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/02_MCAL Multicore_ Module types/image2022-12-30_16-27-56.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "MCAL Multi-Core Module Type IV"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The MCAL module provides interfaces available on any core and one kernel on a single core accessing the mappable element by one core only"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Type IV = 1b + 2a + 3a"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/02_MCAL%20Multicore:%20Module%20types/image2022-12-30_16-28-57.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/02_MCAL Multicore_ Module types/image2022-12-30_16-28-57.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "MCAL Multi-Core Module Type V"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The MCAL module provides interfaces available on any core and multiple kernels on individual cores accessing the mappable element by the according core individually"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Type V = 1b + 2a + 3b"
    }
  ],
